data.description: Experience modern living in this beautifully remodeled 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home, boasting nearly 1,400 square feet of comfortable living space on a spacious, well-maintained lot, a little under half an acre. This charming property is perfect for those seeking a blend of contemporary design and the tranquility of a larger yard. Step inside and be greeted by an open-concept living space flooded with natural light. The recent remodel has transformed this house into a chic haven, where a fresh coat of paint, sleek floors, andupdated fixtures create a welcoming ambiance. The spacious kitchen features new countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample cabinet space, making it a chef's delight. Adjacent to the kitchen, the dining area offers a cozy spot for family meals or entertaining guests. The three bedrooms are generously sized, offering plenty of room for relaxation and privacy. The two modern bathrooms have been updated with stylish tiles, vanities, and fixtures, ensuring your daily routines are both functional and enjoyable. One of the highlights of this property is the oversized detached garage, providing ample space for vehicles, storage, or even a workshop. The large backyard is a canvas for your outdoor dreams, with endless possibilities for gardening, outdoor gatherings, or simply enjoying the serene surroundings. Situated on a quiet street in a desirable neighborhood, this home is conveniently located near schools, parks, and shopping centers, making it a prime choice for families and anyone seeking the perfect blend of convenience and comfort.
